Description:

Developed a structured Employee Complaint Management System within the SMART ERP platform using ASP.NET MVC, C#, SQL Server, 
Entity Framework, and jQuery. Implemented employee complaint submission with category-wise complaint entry, attachment upload, 
complaint details, and employee information mapping. Designed an HR review workflow where authorized users can view complaints, 
verify details, update status, add remarks, and track resolution progress.

Built employee-wise complaint search, filtering, and status tracking features to monitor pending, reviewed, resolved, and 
rejected complaints. Followed a clean Controller–Service–Repository architecture to ensure maintainability, scalability, 
and separation of business logic. Integrated secure data handling, role-based access, and user-friendly screens to improve HR 
complaint processing, employee communication, and organizational transparency.
